3. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possibility as the paper deals with image processing and geometric transformations, which are relevant to graphics applications. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possibility as the paper deals with video processing and motion analysis, which are relevant to multimedia applications.
